{"tid":98582,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[青春回憶] 入黎貼你地部舊款手機","createTime":"2017-01-28T13:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T00:58:45.000Z","uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66608486987012fa556cb951efc0eec2c1d57a61","tid":98582,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T13:38:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ringhk.com/index_phone_spec.php?id=1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Findex_phone_spec.php%3Fid%3D1209&d=fU3nvaAexaWFGJTF6lGlK3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=0c713b8d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ringhk.com/index_phone_spec.php?id=1209</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ringhk.com/sony_ericsson/k550i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Fsony_ericsson%2Fk550i.jpg&h=7616b083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢部咁既爛鬼sony手機<br />\n由小六定中一 (07年) 開始用到2013<br />\n<br />\n雖然話佢爛鬼<br />\n不過俾我用黎發脾氣狂丟好多次都未爆得，算佢好野...<br />\n同埋用左成6年都未壞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我記得以前好努力咁上網搜尋電子書 (好似入左左耳小說入去)<br />\n同埋搵岩呢個手機既game 搵左d爛鬼game 唔好玩既<br />\n<br />\n由於當年冇人想同我互相sms<br />\n所以咩人仔台互send sms全都唔關我事...<br />\n<br />\n仲記得某年用呢部k550i狂上facebook<br />\n結果玩爆左上網費俾左五百幾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喺未有智障手機的年代，傳聞d同學識得櫃筒入面單手打sms<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想當年2010年年尾<br />\n香港岩岩開始流行用智障手機<br />\n阿妹係咁求阿媽話要買手機玩whatsapp<br />\n不過屋企話覺得冇必要就否決左<br />\n咁我又冇所謂，我成個十幾歲都唔鍾意出街，買手機俾我做乜啫...<br />\n<br />\n2013因為升大學全家經常需要聯絡<br />\n所以阿媽買手機個plan送左兩部智障手機<br />\n岩岩好我同阿妹一人一部 (係samsung爛鬼智障手機)<br />\n部爛鬼samsung智障手機就唔貼出黎啦..."},{"pid":"3063d64c7e9bf9af712f7afeba0ecb85f4d9a272","tid":98582,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T13:39:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"951dcc4592bc4c1aed25f838d7fc82d3028387f8","tid":98582,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T13:40:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上網搵圖貼嚟做乜柒</blockquote><br />\n唔知 好悶冇野做"},{"pid":"a281d4e338e6515f19e8deab724591af27a7fa8c","tid":98582,"uid":53775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T13:43:01.000Z","msg":"同樓主同一部，不過跌落屎坑壞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢部幾好用"},{"pid":"7b3eb445d2dd2ce625cce05a12bbb56ab01872c5","tid":98582,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T13:45:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樓主同一部，不過跌落屎坑壞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢部幾好用</blockquote><br />\n呢d舊部手機又冇得上網 又冇乜功能 以前要黎都唔知做乜<br />\n聽歌我又唔係用手機 以前有部好渣既mp3仔"},{"pid":"76648b318cb3b25a25191587b1487af47d82b8c4","tid":98582,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d3nevzfk7ii3be.cloudfront.net/igi/PXZAmQmGON4ABJYL.standard\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd3nevzfk7ii3be.cloudfront.net%2Figi%2FPXZAmQmGON4ABJYL.standard&h=38dbe280&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f127b104ef8c0f829d8a752630c305dbe9fa41d","tid":98582,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T13:56:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://d3nevzfk7ii3be.cloudfront.net/igi/PXZAmQmGON4ABJYL.standard\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd3nevzfk7ii3be.cloudfront.net%2Figi%2FPXZAmQmGON4ABJYL.standard&h=38dbe280&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩開始流行智障手機果陣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cbeb09a9759ec0033727ac2148a61acdfe8ac38","tid":98582,"uid":45,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T13:59:04.000Z","msg":"k800i<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.k800i.de/images/phones/k800i/k800i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.k800i.de%2Fimages%2Fphones%2Fk800i%2Fk800i.png&h=f4d32c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時型到呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後面一啪就影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593bee7ccb53b8b49273fc0c306422547211fa05","tid":98582,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:01:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>k800i<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.k800i.de/images/phones/k800i/k800i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.k800i.de%2Fimages%2Fphones%2Fk800i%2Fk800i.png&h=f4d32c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時型到呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後面一啪就影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你仲有冇SAVE低舊手機影的相 <br />\n而家睇返應該會覺得好朦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41299d9429c50dd0944563bcd4ee1595020af267","tid":98582,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/220335_3cfc947365a77c6bbad79ae1d5a14128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F220335_3cfc947365a77c6bbad79ae1d5a14128.jpg&h=6e52b606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好掛住sms年代"},{"pid":"a1a388514cc93cc09e5551721dda2591123760aa","tid":98582,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.extragsm.com/images/phone/big/Nokia/6280/Nokia-6280-03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.extragsm.com%2Fimages%2Fphone%2Fbig%2FNokia%2F6280%2FNokia-6280-03.jpg&h=129c7512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n窮學生用cheap嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ebf566147fca2ea21958cba352c0f5551ed1e7","tid":98582,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:05:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/220335_3cfc947365a77c6bbad79ae1d5a14128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F220335_3cfc947365a77c6bbad79ae1d5a14128.jpg&h=6e52b606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好掛住sms年代</blockquote><br />\n以前冇人同我SMS"},{"pid":"d3bc3ac4fe3bc5ae3be1d30249671ce8d31e8888","tid":98582,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:06:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://www.extragsm.com/images/phone/big/Nokia/6280/Nokia-6280-03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.extragsm.com%2Fimages%2Fphone%2Fbig%2FNokia%2F6280%2FNokia-6280-03.jpg&h=129c7512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n窮學生用cheap嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n部K550I由中一用到中六 HAHAHA<br />\n不過又冇所謂 如果屋企肯不如換部電腦俾我打機好過<br />\n電腦我由中二開始講左成年<br />\n中三先肯換<br />\n我09年仲用緊WIN 2000 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5986cc5d5647e38b4fce073badcfd886c9531bd5","tid":98582,"uid":29588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:19:19.000Z","msg":"再舊d都係nokia 但已經唔記得 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T594N75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT594N75.jpg&h=67725d78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老竇俾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h78KCXu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh78KCXu.jpg&h=2fcbd0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都係老竇俾 但lag到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dCe7b11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdCe7b11.jpg&h=d4175f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔記得邊個俾 好記得因為係粉紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2465ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2465ss.jpg&h=43a5f443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一部自己買既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係網上揀左好撚耐 覺得最型又唔會太多人用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kfAa81O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkfAa81O.jpg&h=b00271e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上面果部壞左拎去整佢話整唔返直接俾左呢部我替<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cs9Zb8w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcs9Zb8w.jpg&h=57c3a95b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身諗住買iphone但俾sales氹到 話全球首部雙核心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4mk4iaC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4mk4iaC.jpg&h=ae904a9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n果陣唔知咩鳩水貨一野平左好多 從此開始刷rom呀執靚部機(美化?) 慢慢發覺真係無人care....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/221824_53c30cd3bc04508b461563ca70d22292.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F221824_53c30cd3bc04508b461563ca70d22292.jpg&h=a2de74a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用到上個月先換7 plus <br />\n開始做ifandog 懶鳩手機體驗"},{"pid":"492a93baa5e89d97838a0e8b6817af5a5df2bd26","tid":98582,"uid":71728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:20:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://www.extragsm.com/images/phone/big/Nokia/6280/Nokia-6280-03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.extragsm.com%2Fimages%2Fphone%2Fbig%2FNokia%2F6280%2FNokia-6280-03.jpg&h=129c7512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n窮學生用cheap嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前都有部6280 依家放左係櫃桶底 唔見左粒電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外仲用過6670同N85<br />\n部6670 唔見左<br />\n部N85 封緊塵 開得著用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so